long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A shortcut to quickly control input/output of your online calls

Limitation:
* Only support meet.google.com

Features:
* Quickly navigate to the call by click into favicon icon
* Turn the microphone on and off
* Turn the camera on and off
* Turn the sound off the tab on and off
* End the call
